snippet.title: Actress Amber Heard speaks out about Marsha Lazareva case in Kuwait
snippet.description:
Hollywood actress Amber Heard, who is also an official United Nations Human Rights Champion, has joined prominent supporters of the case, including Neil Bush and Cherie Blair.
